name: Good News
description: Good news, take a look. Red whispers with blue, dialectics does not seek conflict, polarities find communication. Isn't that wonderful? Isn't that heartening?  The question is, why red whispers with blue, why must we seek conflict? Why must we strive to create that alignment between opposites that would benefit us all?  Fluent in "as opposed to in."
